Loop Different Decrement Test.

Tests that the ingredient decremented in 'until' can differ from the loop
condition. The loop runs while 'condition' is non-zero (the body decrements
it through the 2nd mixing bowl); each pass the 'until' statement decrements
'counter' instead. Three passes leave counter at 67, served as the letter C.

Ingredients.
3 g condition
70 g counter
1 g unit

Method.
Loop the condition.
Put condition into 2nd mixing bowl.
Remove unit from 2nd mixing bowl.
Fold condition into 2nd mixing bowl.
Loop the counter until looped.
Liquefy counter.
Put counter into mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
